I recently went to the NATIONALS OF INDIA SKILLS 2024 to showcase my talent in PROSTHETIC and MAKEUP and won a GOLD medal representing Uttar Pradesh Farrukhabad at the national level. 
This is the india’s first biggest prosthetic & makeup competition at this high level ., it’s just possible coz of @mesc_india @nsdcindiaofficial @samanthakochharr Maam .❤️

The event was held at @yashobhoomi_iicc  Delhi. 

That India’s Biggest competition was organized by the “National Skill Development Corporation” @nsdcindiaofficial under the Ministry of Skill Development and Entrepreneurship , Government of India.

I was awarded by the Secretary of the Ministry of Skill Development and Entrepreneurship, Mr .Atul Kumar Tiwari; the renowned director of Sholay, Ramesh Sippy; and the famous actor from Stree and Dangal, Aparshakti Khurana.

Out of 2.5 lakh applications from 30 states, 900+ participants were selected for the nationals, with over 60 winning medals in their respective skills.
and some skills and the participants will go Lyon France to showcase the talent @worldskills .

It was an amazing experience overall, where I made new friends from all over India. 
@gowhar_0.2 @shah_kairav @_anjuli.k_ @mua_kajal_saroj @alpeethakurr @sugu364 @make_overbykirti @secret__grin 

A special thanks to the Government of India and the organisers for this event to uplift our youth.
